title: ISic001743. I.Sicily inscription 001743
body:
Facsimile Images

1ΕΝΘΑΔΕ[......---]
2ΠΡΙΑΝΟΣΤΕΛΕΥΤΗ
3ΣΑΤΟΔΕ[..´...]
4ΠΕΝΤΕ´Μ[....]
5ΦΕΒΡΟΥΑΡ[...]
6⳨

Apparatus criticus

Text after Orsi and Strazzulla

English translation

commentary

Orsi - and Strazzulla after him - assumes an unattested name 'Prianos', but more plausible would be 'Koprianos', which is several times attested in the region, with the first part of the name at the end of line 1. Autopsy is required to clarify lines 3-4.

bibliography

  • Orsi 1893 310 no. 132 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715
  • Strazzulla 1897 156 no. 241 https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390
